name: Ftribe Fighters
introduce: Ftribe Fighters (F2 NFT) is building an NFT gaming metaverse where players immerse themselves in an exciting MOBA game experience and earn juicy rewards. its ecosystem comprises Ftribe Fighters, the Multiplayer Online Battle Arena (MOBA) game, NFT Marketplace, Defi platforms, Clash of Ftribe (Idle Game) and so on.
